OL,3,CBrother and friends of Kent Police
OL,4,Cofficer Bradley Corke finish epic
OL,5,Cfundraiser
OL,7,FThe brother and best friends of a Kent
OL,8,FPolice officer who died whilst en
OL,9,Froute to an emergency call have
OL,10,Fcompleted an epic fundraising
OL,11,Fchallenge in his memory.
OL,13,FPC Bradley Corke, who was described as
OL,14,F'caring', 'selfless' and 'committed to
OL,15,Fhis job', lost his life in March
OL,16,Ffollowing a car crash near Dartford.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
