OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1781606875
OL,3,CBrother and friends of Kent Police
OL,4,Cofficer Bradley Corke finish epic
OL,5,Cfundraiser
OL,7,FIf it were not for the Kent, Surrey
OL,8,Fand Sussex Air Ambulance transporting
OL,9,Fthe 27-year old to urgent care, his
OL,10,Ffamily and friends wouldn't have been
OL,11,Fable to spend as much time with him in
OL,12,Fhospital.
OL,14,FUnder three months on from the
OL,15,Ftragedy, his younger brother Nathan,
OL,16,Fand friends Jamie Simpson and Joe
OL,17,FWorsley embarked on the punishing and
OL,18,Fdemanding physical challenge.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1781606875
OL,3,CBrother and friends of Kent Police
OL,4,Cofficer Bradley Corke finish epic
OL,5,Cfundraiser
OL,7,FIn under 24 hours they've climbed
OL,8,Fthousands of feat up three of the UK's
OL,9,Ftallest peaks, Ben Nevis, Snowdon and
OL,10,FHelvellyn to fundraise for the charity.
OL,12,FSo far they've raised almost #10,000
OL,13,Fand are hoping to get more donations
OL,14,Fto keep the momentum going.
OL,16,FClimbing in a changeable, and
OL,17,Fchallenging climate, with just weeks
OL,18,Fto practice, the trio made it to the
OL,19,Ftop of each mountain and set off blue
OL,20,Fsmoke in tribute to Bradley.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1781606875
OL,3,CBrother and friends of Kent Police
OL,4,Cofficer Bradley Corke finish epic
OL,5,Cfundraiser
OL,7,FJamie said, "It was the most
OL,8,Fphysically demanding things we've ever
OL,9,Fdone. Ben Nevis alone took it out of
OL,10,Fus, it was so cold and around -7
OL,11,Fdegrees at the top.
OL,13,F"But we kept pushing and cheering
OL,14,FBrad's name. It was so special."
OL,16,FSpeaking to ITV News before they set
OL,17,Foff from Hastings, where Bradley
OL,18,Flived, the group said Bradley's spirit
OL,19,Fwould push them all the way.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
