SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1781606875
OL,3,CBrother and friends of Kent Police
OL,4,Cofficer Bradley Corke finish epic
OL,5,Cfundraiser
OL,7,FNathan said, "Where the air ambulance
OL,8,Fbrought Brad back for 48 hours when
OL,9,Fhis heart stopped for 30 minutes I
OL,10,Fcan't thank them enough.
OL,12,F"It just means everything to me
OL,13,Fknowing that, you don't have to go
OL,14,Fview the body, he was there, his heart
OL,15,Fwas pumping.
OL,17,F"I know he'd be pushing me up that
OL,18,Fhill. He had that fighting spirit. I
OL,19,Fjust know be pushing us all up and
OL,20,Fcelebrate when we get to the final
OL,21,Fone."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
