OL,3,CBrother and friends of Kent Police
OL,4,Cofficer Bradley Corke finish epic
OL,5,Cfundraiser
OL,7,FJoe said, "As a charity what those
OL,8,Fguys did for Brad and for everyone, to
OL,9,Fkeep him going so he could sense us
OL,10,Fthere, if we were to pay for that
OL,11,Fexperience it's far more than what we
OL,12,Fcould ever raise but to give something
OL,13,Fback as a thank you, and Brad can give
OL,14,Fsomething onto them then it makes it
OL,15,Fall worth it."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/6
